SUMMARY:中国官方非制造业PMI
DESCRIPTION:地区: 中国\n重要性: 3 (高)\n今值: 50.1\n预期: 49.9\n前值: 49.5\n周期: 三月\n详细: 中国官方非制造业采购经理人指数(PMI)\n链接: https://investing.com/economic-calendar/chinese-non-manufacturing-pmi-831\n来源: China Federation of Logistics and Purchasing (CFLP)\n来源链接: http://en.chinawuliu.com.cn/cflp-news/
